SUMMARY:Evaluate Social Media Chatter Options
DESCRIPTION:Research low-cost chatter sources for film domain:\n\n- Bluesky firehose (free\, AT Protocol) — top pick\n- Reddit r/Atlanta\, r/Filmmakers\, r/boxoffice (free tier)\n- Substack newsletters (native RSS\, zero code) — quick win\n- Mastodon film communities (free)\n- Letterboxd (RSS feeds)\n- YouTube comments (free tier: 10k units/day)\n\nConstraint: hundredths-of-a-cent per transaction or free.\nSee ADR-006 for decision rationale.
CATEGORIES:Sprint 7,Research
PRIORITY:2
STATUS:NEEDS-ACTION
UID:predictor-ingest-20260318-chatter-eval@predictor
END:VEVENT
